>
> May 15, 2001
>
>
>
> Northern Border's Gas Control Department has issued a capacity alert for
> the Harper to Manhattan segment effective Wednesday, May 16.  Record heat
> combined with expected high load factors dictates that Northern Border
> schedule only firm transportation in this segment for this gas day.
>
>
>
> Gas Control will evaluate the east end capacity situation on a day to day
> basis and will remove the capacity alert when operating conditions
> improve.
>
> Robert Bryan
> Market Services ,  ext. 7745
